    "119711500": {
      "title": "Generalized Bump-Hoffstein Conjecture for Coverings of the General Linear group",
      "abstract": "In this paper, we investigate the extent to which the Bump-Hoffstein conjecture could be generalized for central coverings of general linear groups. We provide evidence for such generalized Bump-Hoffstein conjecture by proving some special cases."
